Package mae

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationTask
    AnnotationTask serves as a go-between for MaeGui and the SQLite interface TagDB.
    AnnotDB
    TagDB is the class that handles all the calls to the SQLite database.
    AttData
    A class that describes tag attributes that only contain text data (such as comments)
    AttID
    ID attributes have special properties, so they have their own class that keeps track of the prefix.
    AttList  
    Attrib
    The parent class for tag attributes
    DTD  
    DTDLoader
    Provides methods for loading a DTD file into a DTD class
    Elem  
    ElemExtent
    Extents Elem to provide information about tags that are used to label extents in a text (as well as non-consuming tags).
    ElemLink
    Extends Elem; used for describing link tags
    FileOperations  
    HashCollection<K,V>  
    MaeHotKeys
    Contains hotkeys for MAE main Created by krim on 2/17/2015.
    MaeMain
    MaeMain is the main class for MAE; it manages all the GUI attributes and manages how the annotation information is loaded, interacted with, and displayed.
    MaeStrings
    Contains string resources for MAE main Created by krim on 2/17/2015.
    XMLFileLoader
    XMLFileLoader reads in any annotated files that are loaded into MAE by calling the XMLHandler file.
    XMLHandler
